# SubAgent Use Policy

You are free to use subagents as you see fit. Here, I outline any guidelines for how to go about doing so:
- You must always use Composer 2.5 as your subagent model unless explicitly asked by the user to do otherwise
- Never use fast mode.

## Exception

The user's explicit instruction overrides what is written here.
